â€œI am huge indica fan, and other than my CBD strains that I use for PTSD, I manage  anxiety and chronic pain with indicas. I tried some Gas Mask, and wow! Hard hitting body high, melted me into the couch. Great for pain relief, and I slept soundly. Excellent strain for bedtime.â€

â€œFinally got ahold of this strain and oh my god was it worth it. Truly felt as if a mask full of relaxing gas was put on me. â€œIf you are trying to be discreet with your usage this is NOT the strain you want.  This gassy smelling weed can be picked miles away.  Having said that, the taste was much better than the smell.
